BRFSSMissouri 0.1.0
  • Reference

Demographic data from Missouri residents (BRFSS).

Source: R/data_demographics.R
demographics.Rd

A sub-dataset containing demographics information from the years 2023 and 2024.

Usage

demographics

Format

A data frame with 14,528 rows and 18 variables:

SEQNO

key of the dataset

MARITAL

marital status

EDUCA

education level

VETERAN3

veteran status

EMPLOY1

employment status

CHILDREN

number of children in household

INCOME3

income level

PREGNANT

pregnancy status

WEIGHT2

reported weight in pounds

CRACE1

child non-hispanic race including multiracial

CAGEG

child age

AGE80

age

GENHLTH

general health

MENTHLTH

mental health

CHCOCNC1

melanoma or other types of cancer

ALCDAY4

days in the past 30 had alcohol

MARJSMOK

marijuana usage

ASTHMS1

asthma status

Source

https://www.cdc.gov/brfss/index.html
